      "uco-core:description": "Forcible assault involving physical contact with FBI Special Agents J.A. (Count 19) and R.G. (Count 20). Source: PACER Doc 48 (indictment3), Counts 19-20, paras. 66-67",
      "legalproc:statuteCitation": "18 U.S.C. \u00a7\u00a7 111(a)(1) & 2",
